    "ss_testimonial_12_xj7gFi": {
      "type": "ss-testimonial-12",
      "blocks": {
        "slide_D7GMGn": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_style": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3_b6d195a2-9c74-45ef-adef-1c24135fcf56.png",
            "video_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc",
            "controls": false,
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>\"I've struggled with eye bags for years, and no amount of sleep or water ever helped. I was sceptical but after only two weeks, I started seeing a change, I'm now at 9 weeks which is when I took the photo and my bags are SO much better! Way smoother and less puffy. I use them in the evening while relaxing, and I’ve found that the pulsing EMS mode really helps with circulation. I started with 5 minutes at a time and now I use them for 15 minutes, five times a week. It’s an easy addition to my skincare, and I couldn't be happier the results!\"</p>",
            "author": "<p><strong>Caroline S</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_VAxQ8g": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_style": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1_89cd4b24-bb03-4596-a392-f2a466268bf9.png",
            "video_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc",
            "controls": false,
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>\"Let me tell you, I’ve tried EVERYTHING for my crow’s feet, and nothing made a real difference. These glasses, however, have been a pleasant surprise! The fine lines around my eyes and my crows feet have softened dramatically, and my skin feels more elastic. I started with the lowest EMS setting because I wasn’t sure how strong it would be, but I now switch between different intensities depending on the day. The red light is soothing, and it’s easy to use while I’m watching TV.\"</p>",
            "author": "<p><strong>Rachel O</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_pK8tJi": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_style": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/B_A_DG_Glasses_90aa0f3b-c42a-4839-a1cd-6ca006b84937.png",
            "video_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc",
            "controls": false,
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>\"I got these for fine lines and tired eyes, but what really impressed me is how much they’ve helped my hormonal eczema. Since perimenopause, I’d had dry, itchy patches around my eyes that just wouldn’t go away. I was wary of trying anything new, but the red light is so gentle and calming - no irritation at all. After a few weeks, my skin looked calmer and far less flaky. I now use them most evenings for 10–15 minutes and have had fewer flare-ups. It’s such a relief to finally find something that soothes rather than aggravates.\"</p>",
            "author": "<p>Miranda L</p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_98t6xQ": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_style": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/B_A_DG_Glasses.png",
            "video_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc",
            "controls": false,
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>\"It's nice to look awake and refreshed for the first time in years. At 56, puffy under eyes had become the norm for me, until I found these! I use them five times a week, and within a few sessions, I noticed some difference. It was around month 2 when I checked my before photo that I realised just how much of an improvement I'd had... I don't really have eye bags anymore! They're still faintly visible, especially if I'm tired but with makeup they disappear completely. I like to use the pulse on the highest intensity because I really feel it working.\"</p>",
            "author": "<p><strong>Lorraine K</strong></p>"
          }
        }
      },
