          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Read more",
            "answer": "<p></p><p>If you’re in perimenopause or menopause and unsure how to care for your changing skin, you're not alone - and we’re here to help.</p><p>The upgraded DermaGlow Version 2 took over a year to perfect - with 30 prototypes, and input from dermatologists with over 120 years of combined experience.</p><p>We know what skin at this stage of life needs. That's how we know you will look younger, within 60 days, if you use the DermaGlow V2 as advised.</p><p>We're so confident - we'll refund you in full if you're not impressed with your results.</p><p>We asked 500 real customers (all women aged 40-50) why they chose the DermaGlow V2. <a href=\"/pages/5-reasons-why-women-aged-40-50-are-switching-to-the-dermaglow-v2-mask\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"5 Reasons Women Aged 40-50 are Switching to the DermaGlow V2 Mask\"><strong>Read the blog here.</strong></a></p>"
